<div class="title">Suicide Bomber</div>
<div class="substance">Zopiclone (Imovane) & Alcohol</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Wakingdead&Exact=1">Wakingdead</a></div>


